"Prize pool": "",
"Reference URL": "<ul><li><a href=\"https://www.dust2.us/news/54134/media-iem-rio-wont-return-next-year\">Dust2.us: Media: IEM Rio won't return next year</a></li><li><a href=\"https://bo3.gg/news/iem-rio-2025-canceled-brazil-will-be-without-a-tournament-next-year\">bo3.gg: IEM Rio 2025 Canceled: Brazil Will Be Without a Tournament Next Year</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.hltv.org/news/40079/esl-unveils-2025-circuit-pledges-22m-investment-through-2026\">HLTV.org: ESL unveils 2025 circuit; pledges $22m+ investment through 2026</a></li></ul>",
