"Abstract": "Get ready for DreamHack Atlanta, a legendary Halloween gaming festival from Oct 31-Nov 2, 2025! Experience top-tier esports tournaments like CS2 & Street Fighter 6, BYOC LAN parties, and an unforgettable celebration of gaming culture at the Georgia World Congress Center.",
"Approved": "no",
"Category": "esport",
